          "prevention": "Use mobile-specific font sizes",
          "solution": "Implement responsive typography"
        },
        {
          "issue": "Layout broken on small screens",
          "prevention": "Test on minimum supported dimensions",
          "solution": "Use percentage-based positioning"
        },
        {
          "issue": "Controls not responsive",
